Package: sesIndia
Title: Socioeconomic Status (SES) Calculations for India
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates socioeconomic status (SES) using the modified B.G. Prasad and Kuppuswamy scales, adjusted for inflation via CPI-IW. Supports education (1-7) and occupation (1-10) codes, with income ranges updated for January 2025.
